org.jacop.floats.core

Class FloatDomain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jacop.core.Domain
      • org.jacop.floats.core.FloatDomain
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FloatIntervalDomain

    public abstract class FloatDomain
extends Domain
    Defines an integer domain and related operations on it. FloatDomain implementations can not assume that arguments to any function can not be empty domains.
    Version:
    4.1
    Author:
    Krzysztof Kuchcinski and Radoslaw Szymanek
